snippet.textDisplay: Just had my first Astrazenica shot last week. Had it around 6:30pm. No symptoms that night but had crazy, violent dreams. Next day I was good until roughly 4pm and felt like I was getting the flu. Chills, dead tired, achey. Horrible! Went to bed early and felt ok next day.
